      "merge_method": "squash",
      "commit_title": "Adds device-level Top-K Parallel Algorithm to CUB (#5677)",
      "commit_message": "* adds air top-k algorithm to cub\n\n* stylistic improvements\n\n* fixes output offset type in benchmarks\n\n* fixes bit calculations\n\n* caps k to a maximum of num_items\n\n* improves code style\n\n* fixes potential race condition for block load algorithms requiring shared memory\n\n* drops superfluous template param and uses static cta size\n\n* allows making buffer size for intermediate candidates a runtime value\n\n* fixes issue when k==num_items\n\n* makes smem histogram part of temp storage\n\n* makes kth-key-value in identify candidates op to be a ptr\n\n* introduces enum class instead of anonymous int\n\n* style improvements, ceil_div, comments, no-oob-init\n\n* adds subscription factor\n\n* drops oversubscription factor\n\n* refactors filter branching structure\n\n* adds comments, drops superfluous parameters, improves style\n\n* drops more superfluous parameters\n\n* drops superfluous captures\n\n* drops documentation for internal member functions\n\n* drops member var for loading from original input\n\n* improves histo-init\n\n* improves histogram merging\n\n* improves choose_bucket\n\n* drops stream parameter and takes stream from environment\n\n* fixes issue for num_items=buffer_length\n\n* fixes compilation issues regarding bidirectional iterator of transform\n\n* cleans up keys tests\n\n* adds extended fp types to tests\n\n* fixes docs\n\n* renames interface from devicetopk::topk* to just devicetopk::{min,max}{keys,pairs}\n\n* add prints for output keys/values in examples\n\n* removes unused variable\n\n* makes topk selection direction an enum class\n\n* uses dispatch_hub as common interface to dispatch\n\n* fixes keys-only identification\n\n* fixes direction in benchmarks\n\n* fixes namespace\n\n* uses type aliases\n\n* fixes policy access\n\n* adapt tests to take stream via env\n\n* fixes unused var\n\n* wraps stream into env for topk pairs\n\n* fixes clang compilation issues\n\n* fixes clang cuda\n\n* fixes exec specifier\n\n* fixes unused var\n\n* adds ordering and determinism requirements\n\n* fixes msvc\n\n* updates examples to pass requirements\n\n* adds requirements to top-k pairs examples\n\n* adds requirements to top-k pairs examples\n\n* adds api examples\n\n* drops superfluous parameters\n\n* refactors tests; makes direction compile time test param\n\n* refactors topk pairs tests to use compile time direction\n\n* Revise the code according to review\n\n* Use RST style comment\n\n* Use snake_case for variables\n\n* Reword public API documentation\n\n* Extract tuning to separate header\n\n* Remove needless qualification\n\n* Missing qualifier\n\n* Fix identifier naming\n\n* Alias for unsigned bits\n\n* Drop needless comment\n\n* Drop needless qualification\n\n* Drop needless qualification\n\n* Avoid inheriting SelectedPolicy\n\nThere is no need for it\n\n* Replace ctor by aggregate init\n\n* Drop unused datamember: pass\n\n* const\n\n* Small refactoring\n\n* Replace calculate_blocks_per_sm by MaxSmOccupancy + error checking\n\n* Bug fix: query occupancy of correct kernel\n\n* Empty line between functions\n\n* Remove empty lines\n\n* Drop documentation for non-existing parameter\n\n* Const and a few small refactorings\n\n* const\n\n* Eliminate redundancy\n\n* const\n\n* Drop unused captures\n\n* Fix identifier naming\n\n* Drop coefficient_for_buffer in benchmarks\n\n* const\n\n* Small fixes to examples\n\n* Improve example\n\n* Improve benchmarks a bit\n\n* Move environments\n\n* renames indexes to values in api examples\n\n* drops section comments\n\n* strips redundant comments\n\n* drops redundant kernel documentation\n\n* drops clamp in favor of min\n\n* makes allocations array size depend on keys-only\n\n* document perf benefit for unrolled loops where applicable\n\n* drops unused params\n\n* drops histogram param from last filter\n\n* use bool flag instead of cmp nullptr to identify where to load values from\n\n* no_init and skip message for benchmarks\n\n* fixes host vector to be device vector in test\n\n* fixes benchmark exec tags\n\n* fixes default init for histogram\n\n---------\n\nCo-authored-by: Elias Stehle <3958403+elstehle@users.noreply.github.com>\nCo-authored-by: anon <users.noreply.github.com>\nCo-authored-by: Bernhard Manfred Gruber <bernhardmgruber@gmail.com>"
